  "texts": [
    "Finally, the dataset contains key transmission equipment such as transmission towers, poles, and support structures.",
    "Frequent hazards en-GT HQ-SAM OURS (a) GT HQ-SAM OURS (b) countered during maintenance activities are also included, such as engineering vehicles, bulldozers, cranes, and other heavy machinery.",
    "To further enhance applicability, high-impact environmental hazards, such as wildfire and smoke, are also included.",
    "ELE-40K features different imaging condition, including froggy, rainy, and darkness.",
    "Some examples are shown in Fig. 5."
  ]
}